<HEADLINE> Leading World Badminton Rankings </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, September 8 (Xinhua) -- Following are the leading world
rankings issued by the International Badminton Federation on
Monday:
</P>
<P>
Men
</P>
