<HEADLINE> Record Number of Books Sold at National Book Fair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHANGCHUN, September 8 (Xinhua) -- The Eighth National Book
Fair closed here today, reporting a record 509 million yuan (61.3
million US dollars) worth of books ordered and 32 million
yuan-worth (3.86 million US dollars) of books sold.
</P>
<P>
The figures are up 189 million yuan and 8 million yuan
respectively over last year.
