climate in Pakistan as a result of bold economic and fiscal
measures introduced by the present government.
</P>
<P>
The Omani Foreign Minister, who is on a two-day visit to
Pakistan, expressed satisfaction over the enhanced economic
cooperation between the two countries and agreed that there was a
vast potential in boosting the bilateral economic and trade
relations.  
