<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 8 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
today fell four HK dollars to close at 2,982 HK dollars a tael,
according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in Hong
Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 323.4 US dollars a troy ounce,
down 0.14 US dollar from the previous close at today's exchange
rate of one U.S. dollar to 7.7470 HK dollars. 
</P>
</TEXT>
