<HEADLINE> China, Romania Sign Joint Communique, other documents </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 8 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President Jiang Zemin
and Romanian President Emil Constantinescu signed a joint
communique and were present at the signing of four cooperative
documents between the two countries here today.
</P>
