<HEADLINE> NPC Vice-Chairman Meets Japanese Visitors </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 8 (Xinhua) -- Wang Guangying, vice-chairman
of the Standing Committee of the National People's Congress (NPC),
today urged members of a Japanese youth delegation to contribute
