<TEXT>
<P>
SHIJIAZHUANG, September 8 (Xinhua) -- The Huasheng Co. Ltd., a
subsidiary of Huabei Pharmaceuticals, recently opened the world's
largest streptomycete production base in Shijiazhuang, capital of
north China's Hebei Province.
</P>
