1996, with second phase construction completed in July this
year. The quality of the venture's products has met criteria for
pharmacopoeia in all countries, according to a senior manager with
the company.
</P>
<P>
Plans call for Huasheng to account for 65 percent of the
nation's total production of streptomycete.
</P>
