<HEADLINE> Script Design Center to Boost Film Industry </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 8 (Xinhua) -- China recently established a
screen script design center in an effort to uplift its film
industry.
</P>
<P>
The center, which operates under the Film Bureau, is
responsible for organizing talented people to write high quality
scripts, and also purchases stories and outlines which can be
adapted into films.
</P>
<P>
Low payments have created a lack of high quality film scripts
and hindered the development of the film industry. The problem has
been compounded due to a shortage of funding.
</P>
<P>
China has also launched a nationwide program to solicit
scripts, and plans to present awards to the best scripts.. 
</P>
</TEXT>
